com.buschmais.xo.spi.datastore

Interface DatastoreMetadataFactory<EntityMetadata extends DatastoreEntityMetadata<EntityDiscriminator>,EntityDiscriminator,RelationMetadata extends DatastoreRelationMetadata<RelationDiscriminator>,RelationDiscriminator>

  • Type Parameters:
    EntityMetadata - The type of entities used by the datastore.
    EntityDiscriminator - The type of entity discriminators used by the datastore.
    RelationMetadata - The type of relations used by the datastore.
    RelationDiscriminator - The type of relations discriminators used by the datastore.

    public interface DatastoreMetadataFactory<EntityMetadata extends DatastoreEntityMetadata<EntityDiscriminator>,EntityDiscriminator,RelationMetadata extends DatastoreRelationMetadata<RelationDiscriminator>,RelationDiscriminator>
    The metadata factory of the datastore.

    This factory is used on initialization to determine datastore specific entity, property, enumeration and relation metadata.
